(22, 1, '2012-07-20 11:01:00', '2012-07-20 11:01:00', '<p style="text-align: left;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">LIFETIME GIVING SOCIETIES</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span>The IMH Foundation has established Lifetime Giving Societies to honor donors who have provided extraordinary private funding to the Endowment Fund. These gifts include: outright gifts of $10,000 and above, or bequests, life income agreements, life insurance gifts, and gifts of real property valued at $50,000 and above.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="left recognition-list" style="margin-left: 20%;">\r\n	<li>GIVING LEVEL</li>\r\n	<li>(outright / other)</li>\r\n	<li>$10,000 / $50,000</li>\r\n	<li>$100,000 / $250,000</li>\r\n	<li>$500,000 / $1,000,000</li>\r\n	<li>$1,000,000 / $1,500,000</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="left recognition-list">\r\n	<li>GIVING SOCIETY</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Foundation Society</li>\r\n	<li>Founders'' Society</li>\r\n	<li>Order of the Trowel</li>\r\n	<li>Caleb B. Smith Society</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<br class="clear" />\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">ANNUAL GIFT CLUBS</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span> In addition to the Lifetime Giving Societies, annual recognition is provided as follows:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="left recognition-list" style="margin-left: 20%;">\r\n	<li>GIVING LEVEL</li>\r\n	<li>$100 up to $500</li>\r\n	<li>$500 up to $1,000</li>\r\n	<li>$1,000 up to $2,500</li>\r\n	<li>$2,500 up to $5,000</li>\r\n	<li>$5,000 and up</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="left recognition-list">\r\n	<li>GIFT CLUB</li>\r\n	<li>Gold Club Sponsor*</li>\r\n	<li>Quarry Club</li>\r\n	<li>Platinum Club</li>\r\n	<li>Master Builder Club</li>\r\n	<li>Grand Master''s Circle</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br class="clear" />\r\n<ul class="recognition-list" style="text-align:center; width:100%;">\r\n	<li>*Arch Guild - 5 Gold Cards</li>\r\n	<li>Tower Guild - 10 Gold Cards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span>    Memorial Club: any contribution given in memory of a relative or friend. There are a number of ways to contribute to the IMHF to help build for the future of the IMH. </span>', 'Recognition', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'recognition', '', '', '2012-07-24 09:28:29', '2012-07-24 09:28:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/imhf/?page_id=22', 0, 'page', '', 0),
