(205, 1, '2012-08-13 06:40:20', '2012-08-13 06:40:20', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-151" title="Richard J. Elman, P.G.M." src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Richard-J.-Elman-P.G.M.-e1343361366951-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="125" height="176" />\r\n<strong><big>Richard J. Elman, P.G.M.</big></strong>\r\n<em>“Serving on the IMHF Board offers an opportunity to continue what I, as a Freemason, truly believe is the cornerstone of our Fraternity, “Charity.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/CFM.jpg" alt="" width="166" />\r\n<strong><big>Chuck Marlowe</big></strong>\r\n<em>“The Home cannot survive without the work of the Foundation, and as well run as this Foundation is, the Home has a bright future. One can’t say that about all other Masonic Homes—this is why I am proud to serve.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/no-pic-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-164" title="Alex L. Rogers, Vice President" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Alex-L.-Rogers-Vice-President-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Alex L. Rogers, Vice President</big></strong>\r\n<em>“By serving as a member of the Board of Directors of the Foundation, I feel I can provide the necessary commitment and input in re-developing the Foundation’s mission, vision and goals for the betterment of our Indiana Masonic Home.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-166" title="Robert D. Heuchan" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Robert-D.-Heuchan-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Robert D. Heuchan</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I enjoy serving on the IMHF Board because I am able to contribute my time to a valuable Masonic cause and it is a great privilege to serve with such a dynamic group of Masons.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/no-pic-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Greg Jordan</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I have a strong calling to volunteerism and helping others. I am very grateful for my 36-year membership in the Masonic Fraternity. I see this role on the IMHF Board as an opportunity to continue my service to others and it is also a way to pay back (in very small token) all I have received from the fraternity.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-171" title="William A. Sigman, Secretary" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/William-A.-Sigman-Secretary-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>William A. Sigman, Secretary</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I serve on the Board because I believe the Masonic Home is a vehicle to allow our Fraternity to provide a safe and secure home for all members as conditions demand”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-172" title="Michael R. St.Pierre, Treasurer" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Michael-R.-St.Pierre-Treasurer-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Michael R. St.Pierre, Treasurer</big></strong>\r\n<em>“This place we support is where our fraternal obligations live in the everyday activities of our guests within this facility we provide. So may it ever be!”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-173" title="Brian K. Buchanan" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Brian-K.-Buchanan-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Brian Buchanan</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I enjoy being a part of the foundation board as a service to the fraternity and the community at large.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-174" title="James L. Chesney, P.G.M." src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/James-L.-Chesney-P.G.M.-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>James L. Chesney, P.G.M.</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I enjoy working with investments. Serving on the IMHF Board allows me to apply my financial knowledge to help our Indiana Masonic Home. It’s a way of giving back to the Fraternity that has given me so much.”</em></p>', 'Board Members', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-23', '', '', '2012-08-13 06:40:20', '2012-08-13 06:40:20', '', 30, 'http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/30-revision-23/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(206, 1, '2012-08-13 06:50:18', '2012-08-13 06:50:18', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-151" title="Richard J. Elman, P.G.M." src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Richard-J.-Elman-P.G.M.-e1343361366951-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="125" height="176" />\r\n<strong><big>Richard J. Elman, P.G.M.</big></strong>\r\n<em>“Serving on the IMHF Board offers an opportunity to continue what I, as a Freemason, truly believe is the cornerstone of our Fraternity, “Charity.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/CFM.jpg" alt="" width="166" />\r\n<strong><big>Chuck Marlowe</big></strong>\r\n<em>“The Home cannot survive without the work of the Foundation, and as well run as this Foundation is, the Home has a bright future. One can’t say that about all other Masonic Homes—this is why I am proud to serve.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/no-pic-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Alex L. Rogers, Vice President</big></strong>\r\n<em>“By serving as a member of the Board of Directors of the Foundation, I feel I can provide the necessary commitment and input in re-developing the Foundation’s mission, vision and goals for the betterment of our Indiana Masonic Home.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-166" title="Robert D. Heuchan" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Robert-D.-Heuchan-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Robert D. Heuchan</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I enjoy serving on the IMHF Board because I am able to contribute my time to a valuable Masonic cause and it is a great privilege to serve with such a dynamic group of Masons.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/no-pic-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Greg Jordan</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I have a strong calling to volunteerism and helping others. I am very grateful for my 36-year membership in the Masonic Fraternity. I see this role on the IMHF Board as an opportunity to continue my service to others and it is also a way to pay back (in very small token) all I have received from the fraternity.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-171" title="William A. Sigman, Secretary" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/William-A.-Sigman-Secretary-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>William A. Sigman, Secretary</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I serve on the Board because I believe the Masonic Home is a vehicle to allow our Fraternity to provide a safe and secure home for all members as conditions demand”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-172" title="Michael R. St.Pierre, Treasurer" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Michael-R.-St.Pierre-Treasurer-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Michael R. St.Pierre, Treasurer</big></strong>\r\n<em>“This place we support is where our fraternal obligations live in the everyday activities of our guests within this facility we provide. So may it ever be!”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-173" title="Brian K. Buchanan" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Brian-K.-Buchanan-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Brian Buchanan</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I enjoy being a part of the foundation board as a service to the fraternity and the community at large.”</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-174" title="James L. Chesney, P.G.M." src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/James-L.-Chesney-P.G.M.-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>James L. Chesney, P.G.M.</big></strong>\r\n<em>“I enjoy working with investments. Serving on the IMHF Board allows me to apply my financial knowledge to help our Indiana Masonic Home. It’s a way of giving back to the Fraternity that has given me so much.”</em></p>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-160" title="no-pic" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/no-pic-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>George Galyean</big></strong>\r\n<em>"Partnering with the IMH Foundation in service and financial support is an excellent means of achieving our obligation to provide brotherly love and relief to our members."</em>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-164" title="Alex L. Rogers, Vice President" src="http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Alex-L.-Rogers-Vice-President-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" />\r\n<strong><big>Jeff Zaring, Executive Director</big></strong>\r\n<em>"Quisque at elit massa, in blandit est. Fusce purus lorem, dignissim eget condimentum non, fermentum vel odio. Pellentesque vel purus et erat venenatis semper. Nulla facilisi."</em>\r\n\r\n', 'Board Members', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-24', '', '', '2012-08-13 06:50:18', '2012-08-13 06:50:18', '', 30, 'http://www.scxserv.com/imhf/30-revision-24/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
